abstract: Hillary Rodham Clinton has become a master at deflecting questions about her presidential aspirations, but on Saturday she got an early dose of the comedic treatment she can expect if she runs.

headline.main: Clinton Impersonation Steals ‘Saturday Night Live’ Spotlight
